2006-01-31 13:43 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <Ron in xHarbour.com>
  * source/rtl/terror.prg
    + Added new property ::aaStack - array of subarrays of { ProcFile(), ProcName(), ProcLine() }
      /*
         This allows to capture the Call Stack of an error when error is intercepted
         by any error trapping for later processing by outer handler[s]
       */

  * source/rtl/win32ole.prg
    * Safety VariantClear( pVariant ) in hb_oleItemToVariant()

  * utils/xbscript/xbs_harb.ch
  * utils/xbscript/xbscript.prg
    * Refined error handling to [when possible] report the script line of an error

2006-01-31 22:40 UTC+0100 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
  * xharbour/source/rtl/pcre/ChangeLog
  * xharbour/source/rtl/pcre/Makefile
  * xharbour/source/rtl/pcre/config.h
