  * source/vm/dbgentry.c
    ! Fixed a typo which resulted in misparsing of .AND. and .NOT.
      operators.

2006-01-25 18:01 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <Ron in xHarbour.com>
  * utils/xbscript/xbs_harb.ch
